Carter and Tricia

Peter becomes a whistleblower when Carter buys the Pawtucket Brewery and decides to cut corners to save money.

Inside Family Guy

Special episode offering a behind-the-scenes peek at a production week of the series to see what goes into the making of the show.

Gronkowsbees

Football player Rob Gronkowski moves into the neighbourhood. Stewie uses steroids to increase his new bees' honey output, but it makes them aggressive.

Peter, Chris & Brian

Peter watches an old home video and realises that none of his childhood dreams have come true, so he attempts to improve Chris's chances in life by forcing him to spend time with Brian.
